Package nfts

Class NftManager<T extends Nft2D>

java.lang.Object
nfts.NftManager<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class NftManager<T extends Nft2D> extends Object implements Serializable
The NftManager class crucial for managing work with NFTs. Here are NFTs created. And we can also print, get and add to generic array. This generic array is specifically created for NFTs types. Here is also implemented serialization of binary file with NFTs.
